Class LoginResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • shared.communication.LoginResponse

  • public class LoginResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Given a login function call, a login response will be returned to the client. This login in response will contain the username and password previously inputed, in addition to the correctly associated playerID.
